rows.label: tlk42420151_01_msg0001
rows.name:
Chocholo was on the roof gazing up
at the stars when someone stepped
on Chocholo!

rows.label: tlk42420151_01_msg0002
rows.name:
It hurt a lot... Felt like the shoe
was made out of metal.

rows.label: tlk42420151_01_msg0003
rows.name:
So Chocholo asked a Superbia
soldier to find the culprit!

rows.label: tlk42420151_01_msg0004
rows.name:
The culprit maybe too strong for an
ordinary soldier, though... Maybe only
Meleph-sama could really handle them.
